@Cpt s1mm3rYO: as I said, the 1st seed goes to the summer split winner, so if Origen beats Fnatic in final, Origen is the 1st seed. Most points gives second seed.

This is the same for EU LCS, NA LCS and LCK. Only LPL awards the 1st seed to the team with most points (LGD), with 2nd and 3rd being given after a regional qualifier.

